.Dd March 18, 2001
.Dt rezept 1
.Os Koch-Suite
.Sh NAME
.Nm rezept
.Nd Recipe query and export in different formats.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm 
.Op Fl h
.Op Fl text | Fl mm | Fl latex
.Op Fl f Ar filename Op Fl 1
.Op Fl c | Fl i
.Ar pattern
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
requests recipes from the database and formats them in the specified
format.
If no
.Ar pattern
is specified, 
print usage and exit.
By default search for
.Ar pattern
in the
.Em menu-titles .
.Pp
Optional paramters are:
.Bl -tag -width "ALITTLETOLONGFOO"
.It Fl f Ar filename Op Fl 1
Output goes there.
Defaults to
.Em STDOUT .
If 
.Fl 1
is specified, output goes into one single file
.Ar filename ,
otherwise
.Ar filename 
is treated as pattern and a 2-digit counter is appended to 
.Ar filename .
.It Fl h
Print usage and exit.
.It Fl latex
write output as latex-source
.It Fl mm
write output in Meal-Master format
.It Fl text
write output as human readable text. 
This is the default.
.It Fl c
Search for recipes matching
.Ar pattern
in their categories-list.
.It Fl i
Search for recipes with
.Ar pattern
in their ingredient-list.
.El
